title: Race Sport SURVIVAL Series Jump Pack 02JUMP Overview
description:
Race Sport SURVIVAL Series 12000mAh Jump Pack - 02JUMP - http://abt.com/product/84639/Race-Sport-02JUMP.html

• The smallest and lightest portable power with patented technology in the current market.
• Use high capacity and high power battery. Support fast charging low self-disharge cycles can reach 10000 times.

• Multiple safety protection design ensure jump starter zero defect
